{"tid":726411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聲稱放售黃子華棟篤笑門票　青年疑騙約15萬元被捕","createTime":"2018-07-02T11:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T12:34:27.000Z","uid":1886,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3dda6d31bd469d4809e0fd10c1bcd39ccb48bfcb","tid":726411,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"警方星期一（7月2日）凌晨拘捕一名19歲姓麥男子，涉嫌「以欺騙手段取得財產」，正被扣留調查。據悉，有人在網上社交平台聲稱放售黃子華棟篤笑2018門票，收到最少23人支付共約15萬元後，多次藉詞拖延交易。眾事主懷疑受騙，其中一人上月16日報案。疑犯凌晨時分從外地返港時，在機場被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180702/s00001/820b1fb2005fd5bfb783167a11123c83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180702%2Fs00001%2F820b1fb2005fd5bfb783167a11123c83.jpg&h=816080f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00001/1530515206607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00001%2F1530515206607&d=nbPBpL95CC5kiLBe3I2%2Fd8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=9a0cce00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00001%2F1530515206607&h=6aa53155\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00001/1530515206607</a></div>"},{"pid":"3e87ca118ea2bb140ee0117b727e394becb6057b","tid":726411,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"抵9死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30dc146473ebb804bc5d333992d9d568a1862458","tid":726411,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:06:35.000Z","msg":"最少23人支付共約15萬元....<br />\n平均6500...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\